## Components to Build

- Exports & Decision Logs Page
  - UI: Export generator controls (decision selector: single/bulk; format selector: PDF/CSV; include attachments toggle), export settings (branding, signature block, timestamp granularity), export history panel, billing/credit summary, and signing toggle.
  - Data: Current workspace project data, selected decisions, user preferences, and branding settings.

