  - Functionality: Generate time-stamped, authoritative logs (PDF/CSV) including full decision history, option selections, comments, attachments, and firm branding.
  - Signing: Optional signed PDF rendering (digital signature block) for legal use.
  - Output: Files ready for download or delivery to client-facing portal.

- Decision Objects & Approval Workflow (Core)
  - Data models: DecisionCard with options, comments, approval state, audit trail, attachments, and per-decision timestamps.
  - Workflow: State transitions (Draft, Under Review, Approved, Rejected, Finalized), with immutable audit trail entries.

