  - Centralized error messaging system with user-friendly messages, guidance, and recovery actions.
  - Validation routines for export configuration, decision selection, format compatibility, and attachment sizes.

- Branding & Custom Client Links
  - Branding engine: logo, color palette, typography choices, and optional custom domain mapping for client-facing export links.
  - Link management: per-studio branding profiles, domain aliasing, and cacheable assets (logo, CSS overrides).

- Decision Log PDF Template (Asset)
  - Brandable HTML/CSS template that can render as high-quality PDFs.
  - Template sections: cover page with branding, decision options and visuals, audit log (timestamps, user actions), attachments appendix (with file names and descriptions), and a signature page if applicable.
  - Export options: variant rendering for single vs. bulk decisions, and inclusion of attachments.

