- Headings: H1 ~28px, H2 ~22px, H3 ~18px; strong weights
- Body: 15-16px, 400–500 weight
- Layout: 12-column grid with 24–32px gutters/padding
- Cards: White, subtle shadow, 8–12px radius
- Interactive elements: Primary buttons with #0052CC, secondary/ghost styles

